<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂，你也說點什麼吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你<delay20 />有看到嗎？<delay frames="40" />
