<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我叫<tag a="110" b="10" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到能在<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />的慶生會上<delay20 />
還能結交新的死黨，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是喜事連連啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這下就更該慶祝一番啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以後請多關照咧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />慶生會這種活動，<delay20 />
