	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />那傢伙<delay20 />
一副那麼高興的樣子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我甚至想每天都幫<gender3 m="他" f="她" />慶生咧！<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">這生日蛋糕還真大一個啊！<delay frames="40" />
