<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想說你怎麼還不快點送禮物啊！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看看<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />那傢伙！<delay frames="40" />
