<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來幫<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />慶祝生日的嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟生日可是一年一度的重要節日啊，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們就幫<gender3 m="他" f="她" />盛大地慶祝，<delay8 />
